\f0\fs24 \cf0 # CleanPromt \'96 AI Prompt Optimizer \uc0\u10024 \u55358 \u56598 \
\
**CleanPromt** is a minimal, elegant web app that helps users clean, rewrite, and enhance prompts for GPT-based tools. Built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, the app is powered by OpenAI's API and fully deployable on Vercel.\
\
\uc0\u55356 \u57104  [Live Demo](https://www.cleanpromt.com)\
\
---\
\
## \uc0\u55357 \u56960  Features\
\
- \uc0\u55358 \u56800  **GPT Integration** \'96 Real-time professionalization of prompts using the OpenAI API.\
- \uc0\u55357 \u56541  **Live Editable Output** \'96 Edit the improved prompt directly in the interface.\
- \uc0\u55357 \u56594  **Secure API Key Handling** \'96 Uses serverless function to protect the OpenAI key.\
- \uc0\u55356 \u57256  **Clean UI/UX** \'96 Modern, responsive interface with soft visuals and mascot.\
- \uc0\u55356 \u57137  **Lightweight & Fast** \'96 No frameworks. Pure frontend and serverless backend.\
